data.description:
Welcome to your next home at 9180 Sage Loop Ct in Temple, Texas! This cute single-family residential listing is sure to captivate your imagination. With 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half baths, this home is perfect for any family looking for comfort and style. As you step through the front door, you'll notice a spacious living room, providing plenty of space for entertaining friends and family. Featuring a cute kitchen equipped with granite countertops and a convenient kitchen island, it's great for home cooked meals and making memories.
This beautiful two-story home also boasts a spacious backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities.

Located in a great community, you're a short drive to Lake Belton Middle School and Joe M. Pirtle Elementary School, making it convenient for families with children.

Seller will be giving the downstairs living room and stairway a fresh coat of paint as well!!!!!
